title: Contra dance, in the Center
text:
Contra dance, in the Center Oct 20, 2015 
Lincolnville Center — The United Christian Church is sponsoring a contra dance Friday, Oct. 30, from 7 to 10 p.m. at the Lincolnville Community Building, 18 Searsmont Road/Route 173. 
Karl's Dad's Reunion Band will play the tunes and John McIntire will call dances appropriate for all ages and skill levels. All are welcome. 
Admission is $8, with a $20 maximum for families with children. For more information, call John Silverio at 763-4652. 
Courier Publications’ A&E Editor Dagney C. Ernest can be reached at (207) 594-4401, ext. 115; or dernest@courierpublicationsllc.com.
